Achievements.Name: Gamebreaker Possession
Achievements.Description: With the lead FS3 profile, fill your Gamebreaker bar in one possession in any mode except Practice.

Achievements.Name: Hat Trick Hero
Achievements.Description: With the lead FIFA Street 3 profile, score a hat trick with CROUCH in any game mode except Practice.

Achievements.Name: Gamebreaker
Achievements.Description: Score a Gamebreaker goal with the lead FIFA Street 3 profile in any game mode except Practice.

Achievements.Name: Triple Gamebreaker
Achievements.Description: Score 3 Gamebreakers with the lead FS3 profile on the same Gamebreaker in any mode except Practice.

Achievements.Name: Golden Gamebreaker
Achievements.Description: Score a golden goal with the lead FIFA Street 3 profile in a timed match while on Gamebreaker.

Achievements.Name: Gamebreaker Spoiler
Achievements.Description: Score with the lead FIFA Street 3 profile while your opponent is on Gamebreaker.

Achievements.Name: Tourist
Achievements.Description: Score a goal in every environment in any game mode except Practice with the lead FS3 profile.

Achievements.Name: Five-A-Side Match
Achievements.Description: Complete a Five-A-Side match with the lead FIFA Street 3 profile.

Achievements.Name: Challenge Lightweight
Achievements.Description: With the lead FIFA Street 3 profile, complete a match with the Champions.

Achievements.Name: Challenge Middleweight
Achievements.Description: With the lead FIFA Street 3 profile, complete a match with F50.

Achievements.Name: Challenge Heavyweight
Achievements.Description: With the lead FIFA Street 3 profile, complete a match with World Stars.

Achievements.Name: Get Online
Achievements.Description: Complete a ranked or unranked match with the lead FIFA Street 3 profile on Xbox LIVE.

Achievements.Name: Ranked Goals
Achievements.Description: Score 50 goals in completed ranked matches on Xbox LIVE with the lead FIFA Street 3 profile.

Achievements.Name: Ranked Champ
Achievements.Description: Complete and win 25 ranked matches on Xbox LIVE with the lead FIFA Street 3 profile.

Achievements.Name: Host Picks
Achievements.Description: Win a completed match as the host of an Xbox LIVE Playground Picks match with the lead FS3 profile.

Achievements.Name: Guest Picks
Achievements.Description: Win a completed Xbox LIVE Playground Picks match hosted by another player with the lead FS3 profile.

Achievements.Name: Street Fever
Achievements.Description: Complete an Xbox LIVE match against another player who has Street Fever with the lead FS3 profile.

Achievements.Name: Headers and Volleys Match
Achievements.Description: Complete a Headers and Volleys match with the lead FIFA Street 3 profile.

Achievements.Name: Gamebreaker Match
Achievements.Description: Complete a Gamebreaker Goal match with the lead FIFA Street 3 profile.

Achievements.Name: Timed Match
Achievements.Description: Complete a Timed match with the lead FIFA Street 3 profile.

Achievements.Name: Score Difference Match
Achievements.Description: Complete a Score Difference match with the lead FIFA Street 3 profile.

Achievements.Name: Score Match
Achievements.Description: Complete a Score match with the lead FIFA Street 3 profile.

Achievements.Name: Head to Head Series
Achievements.Description: With the lead FS3 profile, complete the last Head to Head match in a best of three of any type.

Achievements.Name: Head to Head Headache
Achievements.Description: With the lead FS3 profile, complete the last Headers and Volleys match to 7 goals in a best of 5.

Achievements.Name: Head to Head Breaker
Achievements.Description: With the lead FS3 profile, complete the last Gamebreaker Goals match to 3 goals in a best of 7.

Achievements.Name: Shooting Gallery
Achievements.Description: Take 50 shots on goal in any game mode except Practice with the lead FIFA Street 3 profile.

Achievements.Name: Wally
Achievements.Description: Run on the walls 50 times in any game mode except Practice with the lead FIFA Street 3 profile.
